Cyberpunk style: A glowing neon-lit server room where streams of luminescent data packets flow like rivers between a massive dark cloud structure hovering above and a compact on-premises server rack below. The cloud is rendered as a swirling mass of electric blue and purple energy, with tendrils of light reaching down like digital tentacles. The server rack pulses with orange and teal circuitry patterns, acting as a relay station. Small robotic helper drones made of chrome and holographic displays hover around the connection points, directing traffic between cloud and ground. Rain streaks across a massive window in the background revealing a dystopian cityscape. The atmosphere is moody with volumetric fog catching the neon glows, creating dramatic light shafts throughout the scene.
